data.title: Official bq Aquaris E4.5 Duo Case - Black
data.meta_description: Protect your bq Aquaris E4.5 from bumps, scrapes and drops with this official flip case in black. - Official bq Aquaris E4.5 Duo Case - Black
data.text:
Designed for the bq Aquaris E4.5

The case is an official bq product and as a result, it features the highest quality materials and also precision cut-outs for the various ports and features of the bq Aquaris E4.5 itself - meaning you won't have to remove the phone from the shell to use it.

Beautifully integrated ultra thin flip case design

The Official bq duo case is beautiful in its design and simplicity; integrating perfectly with the thin body of the bq Aquaris E4.5. The case clips on to the phone by snugly attaching to the rear panel of your device to minimise any extra bulk, and it has a surface cover that gives protection and style to the front of the phone.

Flip design offers comprehensive protection and convenience

As this is a flip case, it offers complete protection for the front and back of your bq Aquaris E4.5. The corners are also protected, so if you accidentally drop it, the most fragile and impact-prone parts of the phone are safe from harm. It also provides quick and easy access to your phone. Simply flip the case open and you have full access to your smartphone's screen.

Official bq product

This flip case is made by bq, so you can be sure of a perfect fit. Using the highest quality materials, the case provides great protection for your E4.5.
